    {
      "id": "18b4750c-f3ba-802b-9b93-d44fef8132ca",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The goal of educational recommender systems is to improve performance. The authors propose a recommender system that uses social tags to build user profiles. Then, it uses Bayes formula to predict next learning materials out of the ones used by similar users (so, collaborative filtering). ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18b4750c-f3ba-802b-9b93-d44fef8132ca",
        "parent": {
